        <Parent_String>skin (collagenous material) [300011840], collagenous material [300192949], animal material [300011793], biological material [300265629], materials by origin [300206573], materials (substances) [300010358], Materials (hierarchy name) [300010357], Materials Facet [300264091]</Parent_String>
